        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/407/508",
        "text": [
          "٤٠٧. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): مَا اسْتَوْدَعَ اللهُ امْرَأً عَقْلاً إِلَّا اسْتَنْقَذَهُ بِهِ يَوْماً مَا."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "407. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Allāh does not grant wisdom to a person except that some day He will save him from ruin with its help."
          ]
        }
